{"tid":2506271,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺仲未有運動習慣既人，真係好可惜  ？？","createTime":"2021-04-27T07:57:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T09:18:47.000Z","uid":123335,"like":11,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e8bd24a85ed55041da0f487925d693c63f4d98fa","tid":2506271,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T07:57:42.000Z","msg":"我都係最近幾年先養成運動習慣，<br />\n以前既我一直冇運動 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解我一直 Keep 住運動？ <br />\n唔辛苦咩？ <br />\n<br />\n其實真係唔辛苦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為你唔需要 Train 到好似運動員咁高強度 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n已經有好多明顯既好處，<br />\n包括：<br />\n1) 精神好左，集中力高左，工作質素大大提升<br />\n2) 心情好左，EQ 高左，交際能力都強左，亦好少有情緒問題 <br />\n3) 好訓左，睡眠質素提升，提升身心健康 <br />\n4) 肌肉量多左，身型 Fit 左 ，著衫好睇左，是但著件底衫出街都幾型 <br />\n5) 食慾控制好左，唔易暴飲暴食，好易 Keep 到體重<br />\n<br />\n...... 仲有好多好處（未能盡錄）<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nd 好處多到果d 乜鳩心血管疾病, 糖尿病 .... etc 風險降低我都講唔晒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff30566a89f262e2ee722cae194576020f058f4b","tid":2506271,"uid":73241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T07:57:52.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"fc804530c1638c9b07cd7edf847fca69c7103f1e","tid":2506271,"uid":384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T07:58:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fce0bb58f7ed01759c3a728601a0604e841d274","tid":2506271,"uid":162558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T07:58:06.000Z","msg":"覺"},{"pid":"ee34a2db23972028666d6fb3594513ee0932f96f","tid":2506271,"uid":5137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T07:58:10.000Z","msg":"Real"},{"pid":"7f37fda51ae753e97d1ac8a6e202e8cad4a724f2","tid":2506271,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-2